# kinema/photo/README 
# Jan.29, 2005
# RIKEN I.Nakagawa


There are several utility routines needs to be improved. 

1. In function CalcCrossSection, some model choises are available,
   but currently these models are selected manually which requires
   to recompile the program. This better be hundled in some external
   input technique. Read comments in the CalcCrossSection routine
   for more detail.

2. In function GetEfficiency, the database file name is hardcorded.
   This function reads in phase space efficiency as a function of
   pion angle theta, which are calculated using other ROOT script.
   It needs to be again developed so that the choise of database
   file can be controled somehow externally. Thus the GetEfficiency 
   function is currently disabled. 
  





